data.title: Azerbaijan`s ambassador presents credentials to Kyrgyz FM
data.meta_description: Azerbaijani newly appointed ambassador to Kyrgyzstan Hidayat Orujov has presented a copy of his credentials to the country's Foreign Minister Erlan Abdildayev, AzerTac state news agency reported.
data.text:
Azerbaijani newly appointed ambassador to Kyrgyzstan Hidayat Orujov has presented a copy of his credentials to the country's Foreign Minister Erlan Abdildayev, AzerTac state news agency reported.

The Kyrgyz minister noted the reciprocal visits of the Azerbaijani and Kyrgyz presidents gave impetus to development of the two countries` relations.

He noted the Azerbaijan-Kyrgyzstan relations were steadily developing. He stressed the importance of expanding cooperation between the two countries.

The Azerbaijani ambassador said that he would spare no efforts to contribute to developing bilateral relations.
